## Environment Variables Configuration

Developers should set these keys inside `.env.local`:

```env
# 1. Database Connection (PostgreSQL or CockroachDB compatible)
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@host:port/dbname?sslmode=verify-full"

# 2. Cryptography Secret (32-byte hex key for GCM encryption)
ENCRYPTION_KEY="your-32-byte-hex-encryption-key"

# 3. Whop Developer Dashboard Credentials
NEXT_PUBLIC_WHOP_APP_ID="your-whop-app-id"
WHOP_CLIENT_SECRET="your-whop-client-secret"
NEXT_PUBLIC_WHOP_REDIRECT_URI="https://your-domain.com/api/auth/callback/whop"

# 4. Feature Control (Disable public community features for single-tenant self-hosting)
NEXT_PUBLIC_DISABLE_LEADERBOARD="true"
```

